      • onItemLongClick

        boolean onItemLongClick(RecyclerView recyclerView,
                        int position,
                        View v)
        Callback method to be invoked when an item in this view has been clicked and held.
        Parameters:
        recyclerView - The RecyclerView where the click happened.
        v - The view within the RecyclerView that was clicked.
        position - The position of the view in the associated adapter.
        Returns:
        true if the callback consumed the long click, false otherwise.
